<section id="pricing" class="section section-muted section-anchor">
    <div class="container"><SectionHeading Eyebrow="Pricing Preview" Title="Practical starting points for planning." Description="Every project is scoped individually. These ranges help you identify a realistic starting budget." />
        <div class="pricing-grid">@foreach (var package in ServicePackages.Pricing) { <article class="pricing-card @(package.Featured ? "pricing-featured" : null) reveal">@if (package.Featured) { <span class="popular-label">Popular</span> }<h3>@package.Title</h3><small>Starting range</small><strong>@package.StartingPrice</strong><p>@package.Summary</p><a href="#contact">Discuss your project <span>→</span></a></article> }</div>
        <div class="pricing-notes">
            <p class="pricing-note pricing-note-highlight"><span>i</span> Prices are starting estimates and may be negotiable depending on scope, timeline, and package.</p>
            <p class="pricing-note">Discounts may be available for bundled services or suitable project scopes. Final pricing also depends on content, features, hosting, domain, and third-party services.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
